Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened after that, Harklight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We conquered the Lake Victoria area from the beachhead created by our Landing Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the combined might of several \NOrbital Knights awed more than just the UE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I would expect this success will have impressed upon everyone the value of a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They had never expected a difficult battle, \Nlulled into security by the power of Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aldnoah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Saazbaum once lamented our stratified society based around the privilege of Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He went as far as saying the emigration to Mars was a mistake in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That power, Aldnoah, allowed humanity to spread to every corner of Mars and start this very war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Asseylum, Princess Lemrina...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Both are victims of Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As are we.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But the days when that power ruled us are no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The land we have conquered shall be the first stone of an empire that spans Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We will combine the power of Aldnoah \Nwith the vast resources that Earth holds,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and build our own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the repairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's looking pretty grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the electrics are fried, \Nand it'll take time to replace them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the times to be assigned a mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're docked, so the Cataphract platoons \Nhave to be sent to the front via landing craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Our two platoons will attack the enemy Landing Castle from the north
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and support the main force \Nattacking from the southwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Special forces" sounds fancy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're little more than cannon fodder here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe HQ figures the chances for victory aren't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that victory include our survival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we need to improve our chances, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaizuka Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can that brain of yours do something about those damned Martians?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Elektris uses electricity as a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Skandia can turn invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both formidable in their own right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't have enough data about Ortygia's replication ability to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky, Ninja, and Houdini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm watching a Sonny Chiba movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What I can say about Ortygia is that he always splits from one into two—never into more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The duplicate always appears within around thirty meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much it splits, \Nthere's probably only one real, piloted unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The others are just copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to seek out the real one \Nand eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the only way is to mark the first one \Nbefore the copies appear and keep track of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We can locate Skandia by raising a smokescreen and monitoring how she displaces it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about Sparky?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One hit from him'll fry your electronics, actuators... the whole shebang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What about insulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That stuff blocks electricity, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you retarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's like, a grade school mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Air is already an excellent insulator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We have nothing that could protect against \Nelectricity powerful enough to go through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The real issue is that these bastards are working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Even one of them would be tricky enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to use your eye again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a mutation code running in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets more and more optimized over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My computing power is even better than it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm, could you change my loadout for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me what I used up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Lemrina,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the invasion of Earth is proceeding according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you could do it, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could say a few words to the knights that have returned from battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My persona, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If Princess Asseylum herself \Nwere to honor their achievements,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it would surely inspire others to serve us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,On an unrelated note, how is my sister's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm told she is still in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is put our trust in the medical staff \Nand allow them to do their work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us pray for her swift recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it get to you.{i'm just gonna creep. down on pumpkin hill i gots to find my lost piece}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I must attend to my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Clydesdale Leader to all units.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Spread out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mustang Leader to Mustang 00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao, what's our plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not finalized, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the coordinates and timings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mustang 11, 22. Move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ortygia Master is our primary target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack together and destroy him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorraia Platoon, advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotland Platoon, flank him west of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorraia Platoon, acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotland Platoon, acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Master is the third from the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think that was the original?{too bad, it's just me, sayaka-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this enemy force to me: Orga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonius Platoon, Pleven Platoon, \Nfocus your attacks on Skandia and destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoke grenades!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The same trick again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unimaginative lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Count Sebring?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us have some fun with them, Countess Raffia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The smoke screen vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Colloids are adsorbed after ionization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how you use high-voltage electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A lightning attack from the invisibility cloak?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,One should die an honorable death in battle, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Any true Cataphract pilot would agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Main force and assault units are in dire straits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this means that the lightning and invisibility units are working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mustang 00, what's your status?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have all the data I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the expanded invisibility field and smokescreen negation were unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you compensate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So they've been waging war for almost two years while I was unconscious.{i think it's like eighteen months and a bit}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And Slaine started that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I will meet with Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You...{da-dow}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you always...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I use my tactical data link to multidimensionally analyze the enemy's movements
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and conjecture their attack habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I then deploy units in positions vulnerable to the enemy's preferred attack patterns
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to bait them into attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is: will my analysis finish in time?{as if it ever fails}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sending you the newest data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Form up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess is that the enemy is right-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He moves counter-clockwise to make it easier \Nto attack enemies to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It sucks being bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Circling around behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing he's withholding his lightning attack \Nso as not to reveal his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he's taken your back, \Nhe should stop for a second to take aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure he's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mustang Leader! Target found!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mustang 00, launching.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dropping you, Mustang 00.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Skandia's leg has been damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It can no longer bear the Elektris' weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Disengaging!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape while I hold them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Target acquired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,#9, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bullets are useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But how about these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What witchery?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Electricity flows via electrical potential difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lightning won't strike something \Nwith the same electrical potential as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're safe from your own attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late. I have the same electrical potential as you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be the infamous orange Cataphract?{Is this the infamous Orange Kool-Aid Man?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Sebring!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sending reinforcements! Just hold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoke grenades!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you kill my brethren!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You will pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Nao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy at nine o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Get as many as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You sent for me, Princess Lemrina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Asseylum—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,my sister—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,has already awoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you do me the courtesy of explaining yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Asseylum's memories have not fully returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed you to continue acting as her, as you have so gracefully done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the new world we are creating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,New world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A world free of worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with no conflict or sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,where everyone can live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And who will ensure the future of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be Princess Asseylum Vers Allusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you really think she wants that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am aware that she does not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is exactly why I will create that world and offer it unto her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,do you know why wars take place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They are a means of negotiation between governments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wars take place because there is someone to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To eliminate war, we must either invade and gain control
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or completely wipe out all opposition so that only one side remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The history of humanity is \None fraught with conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The very instant that Mars split off from Earth, it was inevitable that war would occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I had not done what I had, \NI'm sure that someone, one day, would...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,changed.{ohhhh shiiiiiiii}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the Slaine I knew, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Asseylum?{BWAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:16:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of Asseylum Vers Allusia, first princess of the Vers Empire:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I order you, Count Slaine Saazbaum Troyard, to declare an immediate cease-fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we just needed to take out the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly not the one we marked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it hiding somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I assumed there would be one real unit \Namong them, but I may have been mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistaken? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In my analysis of the duplicates, \NI found out something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment they're created, everything about the master, from position to energy status,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is perfectly preserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he's creating copies via quantum teleportation.{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TaRc43nYfAY}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Except that the original remains intact, thereby creating a doppelganger.{the prestige was a cool film}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But what does it {\i1}mean{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hand over control of all Cataphract platoon targeting and triggers to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Relay request to central command.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Inputting coordinates and vectors for all Ortygias.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How many is he making?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You done yet, Kaizuka Junior?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The targets are multiplying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a second to update.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they ain't gonna sit back and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our ammo won't last!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tactical data link, synchronized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Switching all allied Cataphract targeting to centralized control.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer, Nao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We only get one chance at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're all real...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All targets locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're all real, then all we need to do is blow 'em up at the same time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy Cataphracts annihilated!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm just glad it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't have done it without you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am no longer subject to your authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a citizen of the Vers Empire no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I must take you both into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, message from HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got about two minutes until the laser comms satellite falls below the horizon, cutting us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cutting it close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,On speaker, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Darzana Magbaredge, captain of the Deucalion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Eelis Hakkinen speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Status on repairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nearly done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You will need the equipment on your new mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A mission in the satellite belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be going even higher this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, you'll be briefed later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmission ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The laser's gain has dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Comms satellite is almost out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that doesn't leave us a chance to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like this will be a large-scale battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks he can send us wherever he wants just because we have an Aldnoah Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's equipment for space travel, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A catapult module.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The princesses have been escorted to their quarters with no issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they cannot yet see what you are trying to accomplish, Sir Slaine,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,surely one day—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It matters not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If they wish to remain blind, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Slaine, a ship is approaching the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It is requesting permission to dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a visitor from the Vers homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The blue planet upon which my father sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Count Cruhteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It still bothers me to be addressed by my father's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just call me Klancain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, Count Klancain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:22:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he will be like...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The son of Dr. Troyard.
